ssGUI::​SegmentedVector::​Iterator
ssGUI::​SegmentedVector::​Iterator

This is a Bidirection iterator that allows sequential read for SegmentedVector withouot interfering the cache of it.  Any changes to the SegmentedVector will invalidate the iterator.
